import React,{Fragment} from 'react';
import {Button, Card, Container} from 'react-bootstrap';
const Contact=()=>{
    return(
        <Fragment>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col>
                    <Card>
                        <Card.Body>
                           <form> 
                                <label>Name</label>
                                <input type='text'/>
                                <label>Email</label>
                                <input type='email'/>
                                <label>phone-number</label>
                                <input type='number'/>
                                <button type='submit'></button>
                            </form> 
                        </Card.Body>
                    </Card>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
            
        </Fragment>

    )

}
